definitions.text:
@rỗi hơi
- Waste one's time (on something)
=Ai mà rỗi hơi làm việc đó!+Who can afford to waste his time on that!

@rỗng ruột
- Hollow
=Cây rỗng ruột+A hollow tree

@rỗ hoa
- Thinly and superficially pock-marked
=Mặt rỗ hoa+To have a thinly and superficially pock-marked face

@rỗ
- (of face) to be pock-marked
=mặt rỗ+pock-marked face

@rỗng không
- Completely empty
=Túi rỗng không+A completely empty pocket
